    "description": "State Bank of India Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Financial Analyst for our Kolkata operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout State Bank of India Digital Technologies:\nState Bank of India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with State Bank of India Digital Technologies!",
